    <h2>Customer Service</h2>
    <h3>Order</h3>
    <p>To place an order with Obsequio e Imagen, simply visit our online catalog and choose the productthat best fits your needs. Each item displays the updated price automatically based on yourselected customizations. Through the website, you can request a quote and, if you upload yourlogo, we’ll send you a personalized proposal along with a digital mock-up.Once you receive the design, you’ll be able to review it and request changes if needed.</p>
    <p>After yourapproval, production will begin and you’ll receive a final proof directly from the factory forconfirmation. Once approved, we will manufacture your order and deliver it within an estimated 7to 10 business days, depending on the order specifications.During shipment, you will receive an email with a tracking number so you can check the deliverystatus at any time. If you have any questions or need personalized assistance, our team isavailable by email or phone.</p>
    <h3>Digital Sample</h3>
    <p>Requesting a digital sample is the easiest way to see how your logo will look on the product before it's produced. When you ask for a quote and send us your logo, our team will prepare a personalized mock-up for your review.</p>
    <p>If you need changes, no problem — we’ll revise the design until you’re fully satisfied. Each product has different printable areas. By default, we place your logo in the most common position, but if you prefer another location, just let us know and we’ll adjust the design to suit your preferences.</p>
    <h3>Delivery & After-Sales Service</h3>
    <p>Our standard delivery time is 7 to 10 business days after final design approval, though it may vary depending on the product type, quantity ordered, and chosen customization method. </p>
    <p>Once your order arrives, we recommend reviewing it within a maximum of 7 calendar days. If you notice any issues, contact us as soon as possible so we can provide a swift solution.</p>
    <h3>Cancellations and Returns</h3>
    <p>We understand that unexpected changes can occur. If you need to cancel a confirmed order, please notify us as soon as possible. However, once production has started, it will not be possible to cancel the order, as our items are personalized and produced to order. </p>
    <p>This policy complies with the current regulations, specifically Law 3/2014 of March 27, regarding the right of withdrawal for customized products. In the unlikely event that your order arrives defective or does not match the confirmed design, we will replace the affected items at no cost. Returns are not accepted without a justified reason.</p>
    <h3>Payment Methods</h3>
    <p>We offer the following payment methods for your convenience: - Bank transfer, commonly used for business transactions due to its traceability and security. - Credit card payment.</p>
    <p>If you choose this option, we will provide a secure link upon confirmation of your order. For large orders, we offer the possibility to arrange partial payments by bank transfer. Please contact our team to coordinate this option.</p>
    <p>The previously agreed payment method is also 
available for clients who are already registered in our system. 
</p>
    <h3>Free Sample Policy</h3>
    <p>We know how important it is to evaluate a product before making a significant order. That’s why we offer a free sample service in most cases. If you request several samples or items of high value, we will inform you in advance of any associated cost so you can decide whether to proceed with the shipment. </p>
    <p>To request a sample, please email comercial@obsequioeimagen.com, indicating the product name, your contact details, and the delivery address.</p>
